- Digital energy-efficiency systems: Trip Optimizer™ smart cruise control (deployed at scale; >1 billion miles/huge fuel savings aggregate; EPA-certified fuel-saving technology) and other digital systems (AI/automation for operations, railcar tracking, yard inspections). These are proven, productized software solutions that reduce fuel consumption and operating emissions for customers. [Wabtec corporate](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFlAfCqwi7RZ5bAkw24e6t_FMdO-mpCVDIPfA_Yt1-hTNIpo2dVkJMLCrnkHcNDB72KLBDhdTOBDqmvnTAcSBiuRxSLXeYW6vjdrYeO7LRCx7J87ynEn1DoeA45TU0f2F0CBuzBab19W-VEg9fgWIG-F8kODHvKYegbsNCtpzcOtzAtnWQ9Hn9APHso) [railwayage](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEnR_mC_-tbnvQ6iTtbtlIamk5v1doN0NEfz1n0D4ErsE5M_W8hmMysWAha2wglUhUs8M0zMP11zENHSvQCsEN8PdwpysnVusHOdzLiS4etO_XOxtaf7wGgkPS49G2Pkdvsj_vB) [ainvest](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEZaXjTzRa0hNfCVs2pasGgfpncCopAmZ93N0Nn907NW1MbXdRjHewQFWfwkZlTOFT73eWI6F0YwCDSjmSR2e7BR8QIJfUDfjzUZzjTF9LO0Dl0d-hZ-04VLyQgUy_2YTY_2syYjTzGpPZr6SKBS-b390FnwZO8ToscWvX029yt8NX1-aMDFaIidlnKtP5Ht2uUsvBcfTgRlbYHhCO72KS2EoU6-0GWsN_yBqxXSkBINgctkReQt6x4YT0knCRg2xjnE9sG7t6l).
