Why 19/25: Wabtec has multiple advanced sustainable technologies deployed with real customer orders and site implementations (battery locomotives, Trip Optimizer, remanufacturing, alternative-fuel capability). These are significant and operationally integrated across customers and Wabtec sites, but many battery/hydrogen deployments remain in staged rollouts or pilot-to-commercial phases (so while “implemented” and scaling, not yet uniformly large-scale worldwide). See FLXdrive customer list and production schedules. [railway-technology](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEsal3cQUxYgNH9z9W5msDrXqbxCoNcAfROfclT1JYIP2AXYu7PCKCAYH4de90zDfwoqsu2_13bVeWu602RL3iTN9FVuG6oE38XjHPYi5V5Pyp2-BKc-3AFwAjRwxwTLstce2lnWHeNMd18P_ILAhX716IpL3abXQC7qQ==) [trains](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGC-HdQxbB80WJ_jYfQVDTCQkI0k3GU2uRGApF6psrRgsAswtEiflS3hTcUYtptfHEMTbXckde4znbaDkEdsWuo342098kToKTF6gnx0JMOKrzpSl_ndZf1uRot1b7xVrni7N-81i7z11Yb0l4e1cqMPFMavvmFDAux9rpvkXw7gvEAbN9h84QqpRgS5ZqGtHnVP0Ft1ViRgR1Qa75tfTMNusYeB59bLk1t) [wabteccorp](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGskbU2MFk2lJDfN9mctarGG48TOvewvY6WhIO0Ta7sYvAlWjWIJyXMr03mKsxLb80OQRw9WuQLtmYrIGaFCG25izkidJbzp6J3Kf0GTaenZd0VOihYuqvGlgGy3ehs7bvMqfUJFzPcsYWLg0VHEyB9LQPhrN4W3eQK3M1km9oC_9vDSBOUWkIPlhgl8TJPPz9bYXHrOiCrLLaYiKli2u0oi1Xr7i5jVY73h_r1RVjkWMUjRG6p1A==).

